---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.jsx";
import { withBase } from "../utils/basePath";

const heroLetters = withBase("/images/memorial-letters.webp");
const heroImage = withBase("/images/memorial-foreground.png");
const accordionItems = [
  {
    title: "Como trabajamos",
    body:
      "Leemos con metodo, contrastamos fuentes y convertimos el archivo en piezas claras: efemerides, ensayos, rutas y notas de presente. Cada texto busca separar memoria de ruido.",
  },
  {
    title: "Que nos mueve",
    body:
      "Nos mueve una idea sencilla: el Imperio Espanol merece una lectura exigente, sin nostalgia facil y sin consigna. Queremos recuperar contexto, instituciones, disciplina y legado.",
  },
  {
    title: "Donde creamos",
    body:
      "La web sostiene el archivo; la comunidad abre la conversacion. Entre articulos, manifiesto, biblioteca y mentidero construimos una mesa comun para estudiar la historia del Siglo de Oro de Espana.",
  },
];
---

<Layout
  title="Memorial"
  description="Sobre Imperio Espanol: archivo vivo, comunidad y memoria historica con metodo."
>
  <Navigation />
  <script is:inline>
    document.body.classList.add("preloader-done", "memorial-nav-ready");
  </script>

  <main class="memorial-page">
    <section class="memorial-hero" aria-labelledby="memorial-title">
      <h1 id="memorial-title" class="memorial-title">
        <img src={heroLetters} alt="MEMORIAL" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
      </h1>
      <div class="memorial-figure" aria-label="Formacion historica del Imperio Espanol">
        <img src={heroImage} alt="" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="memorial-intro" aria-label="Introduccion">
      <p>
        Contactanos en nuestro apartado de contacto
      </p>
      <a class="memorial-contact" href={withBase("/contacto")}>CONTACTO</a>
    </section>

    <section class="memorial-copy" aria-label="Sobre nosotros">
      <p>
        Imperio Espanol nace como un archivo vivo de ideas y memoria. No queremos
        levantar una vitrina inmovil, sino una mesa de trabajo donde historia,
        presente y comunidad puedan encontrarse con sobriedad.
      </p>
      <p>
        Nuestro oficio es leer el largo plazo: instituciones, decisiones, rutas,
        victorias, heridas y permanencias. Lo hacemos con articulos breves,
        rutas tematicas, biblioteca, manifiesto y debate compartido.
      </p>
      <p>
        Aqui la memoria no es decorado. Es criterio. Sirve para pensar el
        presente sin ruido, para ordenar preguntas y para recordar que una
        comunidad tambien se construye alrededor de lo que decide estudiar.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="memorial-accordions" aria-label="Ejes del proyecto">
      {accordionItems.map((item) => (
        <details class="memorial-accordion">
          <summary>
            <span>{item.title}</span>
            <span class="memorial-plus" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p>{item.body}</p>
        </details>
      ))}
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .memorial-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: clamp(6.2rem, 9vw, 8rem) clamp(1rem, 4vw, 5.2rem) clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 18%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.035) 0 1px, transparent 1px),
      radial-gradient(circle at 72% 40%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03) 0 1px, transparent 1px),
      #fbfbfa;
    background-size: 13px 13px, 19px 19px, auto;
    color: #050505;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav) {
    --nav-links-progress: 1 !important;
    --nav-gradient-top-alpha: 0.92 !important;
    --nav-gradient-bottom-alpha: 0.78 !important;
    --nav-gradient-stop: 100% !important;
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
    pointer-events: auto;
  }

  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .main-nav__links) {
    opacity: 1 !important;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }

  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .main-nav__links-wrap) {
    opacity: 1 !important;
    visibility: visible !important;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }

  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .main-nav__link) {
    color: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.98);
  }

  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .nav-links-cluster) {
    gap: clamp(0.7rem, 1.8vw, 2.2rem);
  }

  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .nav-link) {
    --nav-hover-mark-size: clamp(0.78em, 0.7em + 0.18vw, 1em);
    --nav-hover-mark-gap: clamp(0.26rem, 0.46vw, 0.58rem);
    --nav-hover-mark-offset: clamp(0.14rem, 0.24vw, 0.32rem);
    position: relative;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0 calc(var(--nav-hover-mark-gap) + var(--nav-hover-mark-size) * 0.55);
  }

  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .nav-link::before),
  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .nav-link::after) {
    content: "[";
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 0;
    transform: translate(calc(var(--nav-hover-mark-offset) * -1), -50%);
    color: var(--color-red-accent);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    font-size: var(--nav-hover-mark-size);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .nav-link::after) {
    content: "]";
    left: auto;
    right: 0;
    transform: translate(var(--nav-hover-mark-offset), -50%);
  }

  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .nav-link:hover),
  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .nav-link:focus-visible) {
    color: var(--color-red-accent);
  }

  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .nav-link:hover::before),
  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .nav-link:hover::after),
  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .nav-link:focus-visible::before),
  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav .nav-link:focus-visible::after) {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translate(0, -50%);
  }

  :global(body.memorial-nav-ready #main-nav:not(.main-nav--menu-revealed) .menu-button) {
    color: #111;
    mix-blend-mode: normal;
    transition-delay: 0s;
  }

  .memorial-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: clamp(22rem, 50vw, 43rem);
    margin-top: clamp(0.5rem, 1vw, 1rem);
  }

  .memorial-title {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: min(96vw, 1400px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 0;
    transition: z-index 0s linear;
  }

  .memorial-title:hover,
  .memorial-title:focus-within {
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .memorial-title img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: clamp(5rem, 13vw, 11.8rem);
    object-fit: contain;
    transform-origin: center;
    transition: transform 0.42s cubic-bezier(0.2, 1.28, 0.32, 1);
    will-change: transform;
  }

  .memorial-title:hover img,
  .memorial-title:focus-within img {
    transform: scale(1.035);
  }

  .memorial-figure {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: clamp(-1.2rem, 1.8vw, 1.8rem);
    z-index: 2;
    width: min(98vw, 1448px);
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .memorial-figure::before,
  .memorial-figure::after {
    content: none;
  }

  .memorial-figure img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: clamp(22rem, 48vw, 46rem);
    object-fit: contain;
    opacity: 1;
    filter: none;
  }

  .memorial-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: clamp(-2.4rem, -3vw, -0.7rem);
  }

  .memorial-intro p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #050505;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.3vw, 1.25rem);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .memorial-intro strong {
    color: #ff351a;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .memorial-contact {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 3.4rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.85rem;
    background: #050505;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1vw, 1.08rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .memorial-contact:hover,
  .memorial-contact:focus-visible {
    background: #ff351a;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .memorial-copy {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    margin-top: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 4.8rem);
    padding-top: clamp(1.4rem, 2.2vw, 2rem);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
  }

  .memorial-copy p {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.74);
    font-size: clamp(1.04rem, 1.32vw, 1.24rem);
    line-height: 1.42;
  }

  .memorial-accordions {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: clamp(1.2rem, 3.4vw, 3.2rem);
    margin-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
  }

  .memorial-accordion {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
    color: #050505;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .memorial-accordion[open] {
    border-top-color: #ff351a;
  }

  .memorial-accordion summary {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 4.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    list-style: none;
    color: #050505;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .memorial-accordion summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .memorial-accordion[open] summary {
    color: #ff351a;
  }

  .memorial-plus {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 2.4vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1;
    color: currentColor;
    transition: color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .memorial-accordion[open] .memorial-plus {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .memorial-accordion p {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    color: #ff351a;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.48;
    padding-right: clamp(0rem, 2vw, 2.4rem);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .memorial-page {
      overflow: visible;
    }

    .memorial-hero {
      min-height: clamp(18rem, 62vw, 31rem);
    }

    .memorial-title {
      width: min(100vw, 900px);
    }

    .memorial-title img {
      max-height: clamp(3.8rem, 15vw, 7.2rem);
    }

    .memorial-figure {
      top: clamp(-0.8rem, 3.4vw, 1.8rem);
      width: min(112vw, 900px);
    }

    .memorial-intro,
    .memorial-copy,
    .memorial-accordions {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    }

    .memorial-contact {
      width: fit-content;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .memorial-page {
      padding: 5.6rem 1rem 2rem;
    }

    .memorial-hero {
      min-height: 18rem;
    }

    .memorial-figure {
      width: 112vw;
      top: 0rem;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }

    .memorial-copy {
      margin-top: 2.2rem;
    }

    .memorial-accordion summary {
      min-height: 4rem;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
